Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.34,0:01:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  贵志  你来看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.56,0:01:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买了这么多零食
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很多啊  塔子婶婶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带去参加习题合宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:01:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后这包薯片装不进去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  现在就解决了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:02:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你替别人着想的方式真够笨拙的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你也来帮忙吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  老是要人操心
